Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式开始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 孩子们拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？
