Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我们去哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去启动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 救世主登场了
