Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又与我作对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从上面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地球联邦政府宣战
